<h1 style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:22px;line-height:1.3;color:#202020;">New brand request</h1>

<p style="margin:0 0 12px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;color:#4b5563;">
  A seller submitted a new brand request while creating or updating a product.
</p>

<ul style="margin:0 0 16px 18px;padding:0;color:#202020;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;">
  <li><strong>Brand:</strong> <%= brandTitle %></li>
  <li><strong>Brand slug:</strong> <%= brandSlug %></li>
  <li><strong>Seller:</strong> <%= vendorName %></li>
  <% if (productTitle) { %><li><strong>Product:</strong> <%= productTitle %></li><% } %>
  <% if (productId) { %><li><strong>Product ID:</strong> <%= productId %></li><% } %>
  <% if (requestId) { %><li><strong>Request ID:</strong> <%= requestId %></li><% } %>
</ul>

<p style="margin:0;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;color:#4b5563;">
  Review this request and either link it to an existing canonical brand or approve a new brand record.
</p>
